message.content: Use the get_fact tool for both 'cactus' and 'swift', then summarize both facts.
{"name":"get_fact","content":"Cacti store water in thick stems to survive arid climates."}
{"name":"get_fact","content":"Swift is a type-safe language that emphasizes expressive syntax and performance."}

The cactus stores water in its thick stems to survive arid environments. Swift is a type-safe language known for its expressive syntax and strong performance, commonly used for developing iOS applications. Both facts highlight unique adaptations: one biological and the other technical.
